'''Automated laser traps''' were [[Laser/Legends|lasers]] that were attached to a sensor set for automated targeting. [[Laser/Legends|Laser]] traps were used in the [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star]] detention level.

The most common kind of laser trap was the [[BlasTech Industries/Legends|BlasTech]] [[Class VI automated laser projector]]. It had a small control computer, a [[Sensor/Legends|sensor]] suite, and a small laser. It could be controlled automatically or through a remote.

